{
  "texts": [
    "Second, we hypothesized that chunk embeddings would perform worse than CLEAR when the parts of the note retrieved by CLEAR were ranked lower by the chunk embedding model.",
    "To do this, we calculated the chunk embedding model ranking of the chunk that overlapped most with the CLEAR chunk (as measured by ROUGE-L).",
    "For NER, we relied on Flan-T5-XXL.",
    "Augmentation used GPT-4.",
    "Our entity selection cosine similarity model was Bio+ClinicalBERT, and the entity filtering LLM was GPT-4."
  ]
}